  "texts": [
    "Specifically, we have three graph neural networks (GCN [20], GAT [21], and Graph Transformer [22]).",
    "We also deploy the large language model (Chatgpt-3.0) to directly predict the MBTI types based on generated(a) Follower Count (b) Group Size descriptions.",
    "Since our framework is compatible with any hypergraph neural network, we also introduce another hypergraph model (HGNNP [23]) in our framework to see the universality of our approach.",
    "We use Adam optimizer with a learning rate of 0.001, weight decay 5e-4.",
    "We set max training epochs as 500."
  ],
